| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0243 — Recovery Inhibition (pear)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 340a56ae-d373-5c67-b2d8-9eab844a933b"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
